******************************************************************
    DESCRIPTION
******************************************************************

    This module provides a method to save and re-use configurations
    of the Primer Theme (http://drupal.ncsu.edu).

    Permitted users can save their current settings, or use an
    existing configuration.

    Configuration are available from two sources:

        1. Local configurations
            * Saved in the database table with the "configKey"
              value having a prefix of local_
            * These are managed by the individual site and are
              are not available for other site owners to use
            
        2. Global configurations
            * Saved in the database table with the "configKey"
              value having a prefix of global_
            * These are managed by the NC State Drupal administrator
              site and are available for other site owners to use
            * Global configurations will be added to this module
              periodically so that they are available it is upgraded
          

 
